Real-Time Stock Portfolio P&L Tracker
Python (Colab) + Power BI Dashboard Project

A complete end-to-end project that fetches real-time stock prices, calculates P&L, builds sensitivity analysis, and visualizes everything through a professional Power BI dashboard.

This project is built for financial analytics, trading insights, and portfolio monitoring.

